QuestData.Title: Back Through the Waygate
QuestData.Description: You speak the truth, $r. I can sense the very essence of Sholazar Basin begin to fray by the blight of undeath even as we speak.$B$BI've bound my being into the rune, $r. Deliver it to she who sent you here -- for only her power can grant me passage to her lands.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Omega Rune to the Avatar of Freya at the Rainspeaker Rapids in Sholazar Basin.
QuestData.RewardText: You've done well.$B$BWoe unto our enemies. Woe unto those who serve the Lich King and threaten the titans' creations -- for the Etymidian is here.
